				<td colspan="2"><span>another aspect you shouldnt overlook. usually it doesnt matter, if a song drops a very short time, the overall benefit of 4 songs that are 95 % active is worth alot more than 3 songs that are up 100 % of the time.
<br />
things may vary in certain spots where 100 % resists/mes/oos for example are needed timewise.
<br />

<br />
and i would suggest to setup different hotkey banks, so you can always use the keys 1 to 4 for your twist, and just switch the hotkeybank, if needed. 
<br />

<br />
personally i have my standard group setup on bank 2 (chorus, warsong, rizlonas, veeshans)and switch to 4 when i need to mes(mes, chorus, warson, riz).
<br />

<br />
hope that helps a bit!</span></td>
